---
import Subheading from '../Subheading.astro';
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
import Service1 from '../../assets/Images/Service1.jpeg';
import Service2 from '../../assets/Images/Service7.jpeg';
import Service3 from '../../assets/Images/Service3.jpeg';
import Service4 from '../../assets/Images/Service2.jpeg';
import Service5 from '../../assets/Images/whyusimage.jpeg';
const { title } = Astro.props;
---

<section class="relative bg-lt-gray">
	<div class="pt-10 pb-11.5 sm:pt-14 sm:pb-11.5">
		<Subheading title={title} />
		<div
			class="max-w-180 xl:max-w-[92%] flex flex-col items-center my-0 mx-auto px-7.5"
		>
			<div
				class="relative w-full mt-9.25 mb-1 sm:py-0 sm:px-7.5 sm:w-195 sm:max-w-195 sm:my-7.5 flex flex-col items-center justify-center"
			>
				<span
					class="mt-5 mb-10 flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center sm:items-start relative m-0 p-7.5 w-full text-left rounded-xl shadow-[2px_2px_14px_rgba(0,0,0,0.2)]"
					><div
						class="mb-5 shrink-0 sm:me-6.5 w-37.5 h-37.5 overflow-hidden rounded-xl"
					>
						<Image
							src={Service1}
							alt="Fix  your books"
							class="object-cover w-full h-full"
						/>
					</div>
					<div
						class="relative -top-1 items-center sm:items-start flex flex-col justify-center w-full h-full"
					>
						<div
							class="text-[19px] sm:text-[22px]! mt-0 font-bold sm:font-medium text-center sm:text-left normal-case py-0 px-0"
						>
							What does bookkeeping cleanup involve?
						</div>
						<div
							class="px-0 py-0 text-center text-[16px]! leading-[1.7] sm:text-left sm:text-lg sm:leading-[1.55] mt-2.5"
						>
							Bookkeeping cleanup entails reviewing your financial records,
							correcting errors, and organizing past transactions to ensure
							everything is accurate and up-to-date. This process helps make
							your accounting practices efficient moving forward.
						</div>
					</div>
				</span>
				<span
					class="mt-5 mb-10 flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center sm:items-start relative m-0 p-7.5 w-full text-left rounded-xl shadow-[2px_2px_14px_rgba(0,0,0,0.2)]"
					><div
						class="mb-5 shrink-0 sm:me-6.5 w-37.5 h-37.5 overflow-hidden rounded-xl"
					>
						<Image
							src={Service2}
							alt="Clean up"
							class="object-cover w-full h-full"
						/>
					</div>
					<div
						class="relative -top-1 items-center sm:items-start flex flex-col justify-center w-full h-full"
					>
						<div
							class="text-[19px] sm:text-[22px]! mt-0 font-bold sm:font-medium text-center sm:text-left normal-case py-0 px-0"
						>
							How long does the bookkeeping cleanup process usually take?
						</div>
						<div
							class="px-0 py-0 text-center text-[16px]! leading-[1.7] sm:text-left sm:text-lg sm:leading-[1.55] mt-2.5"
						>
							The length of the cleanup process depends on the volume and
							complexity of your financial records. Generally, we provide a time
							estimate after an initial assessment, ensuring you have a clear
							understanding before we begin.
						</div>
					</div>
				</span>
				<span
					class="mt-5 mb-10 flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center sm:items-start relative m-0 p-7.5 w-full text-left rounded-xl shadow-[2px_2px_14px_rgba(0,0,0,0.2)]"
					><div
						class="mb-5 shrink-0 sm:me-6.5 w-37.5 h-37.5 overflow-hidden rounded-xl"
					>
						<Image
							src={Service3}
							alt="Help with QuickBooks"
							class="object-cover w-full h-full"
						/>
					</div>
					<div
						class="relative -top-1 items-center sm:items-start flex flex-col justify-center w-full h-full"
					>
						<div
							class="text-[19px] sm:text-[22px]! mt-0 font-bold sm:font-medium text-center sm:text-left normal-case py-0 px-0"
						>
							Can you help with bookkeeping cleanup even if I'm not currently
							using QuickBooks?
						</div>
						<div
							class="px-0 py-0 text-center text-[16px]! leading-[1.7] sm:text-left sm:text-lg sm:leading-[1.55] mt-2.5"
						>
							Yes! Our team is experienced with various accounting software and
							can assist with cleanup regardless of the system you are using. We
							can help migrate your data safely to QuickBooks if you decide to
							switch later.
						</div>
					</div>
				</span>
				<span
					class="mt-5 mb-10 flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center sm:items-start relative m-0 p-7.5 w-full text-left rounded-xl shadow-[2px_2px_14px_rgba(0,0,0,0.2)]"
					><div
						class="mb-5 shrink-0 sm:me-6.5 w-37.5 h-37.5 overflow-hidden rounded-xl"
					>
						<Image
							src={Service4}
							alt="Help with QuickBooks"
							class="object-cover w-full h-full"
						/>
					</div>
					<div
						class="relative -top-1 items-center sm:items-start flex flex-col justify-center w-full h-full"
					>
						<div
							class="text-[19px] sm:text-[22px]! mt-0 font-bold sm:font-medium text-center sm:text-left normal-case py-0 px-0"
						>
							Will my financial data be secure during the cleanup?
						</div>
						<div
							class="px-0 py-0 text-center text-[16px]! leading-[1.7] sm:text-left sm:text-lg sm:leading-[1.55] mt-2.5"
						>
							Absolutely! We take your data security very seriously and follow
							best practices to ensure your financial information is protected
							throughout the cleanup process.
						</div>
					</div>
				</span>
				<span
					class="mt-5 mb-10 flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center sm:items-start relative m-0 p-7.5 w-full text-left rounded-xl shadow-[2px_2px_14px_rgba(0,0,0,0.2)]"
					><div
						class="mb-5 shrink-0 sm:me-6.5 w-37.5 h-37.5 overflow-hidden rounded-xl"
					>
						<Image
							src={Service5}
							alt="Help with QuickBooks"
							class="object-cover w-full h-full"
						/>
					</div>
					<div
						class="relative -top-1 items-center sm:items-start flex flex-col justify-center w-full h-full"
					>
						<div
							class="text-[19px] sm:text-[22px]! mt-0 font-bold sm:font-medium text-center sm:text-left normal-case py-0 px-0"
						>
							What are the signs that I need a bookkeeping cleanup?
						</div>
						<div
							class="px-0 py-0 text-center text-[16px]! leading-[1.7] sm:text-left sm:text-lg sm:leading-[1.55] mt-2.5"
						>
							If you notice discrepancies in your financial reports, missed tax
							deadlines, or if you're feeling overwhelmed by your bookkeeping
							processes, it may be time for a bookkeeping cleanup to get back on
							track.
						</div>
					</div>
				</span>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>
